府係有誠意取消就合情合理合法地撤回整個法案<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性 - 沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者 - 沒有特首強推送終條例，何來市民上街示威，更唔會比警察拉<br />\n<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件 - 全世界都知香港黑警濫權同警黑合作的問題<br />\n<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選 - 最重要一點，一切問題起源，就係特首並非由市民選出，特首不能代表市民意願，不以民為本，只為中央考慮<br />\n<br />\n因此，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n8.5大罷工"},{"pid":"4d77b04cc009fa5613f682993cd41b6ccc3549c9","tid":1392550,"uid":144453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrUPMf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrUPMf5.jpg&h=2f5cb50e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"221dd03d74ef486b94f8cfa8af8d4eb3aef92a87","tid":1392550,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"驚撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca22615db7d0ffb12281e944bc6e81334d6b6f0","tid":1392550,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"警狗個屌老母集會呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c339380fa7e86083482f866bc53a066013322026","tid":1392550,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"又唔見佢拎本警例嚟講?<br />\n敵人反對的就要擁護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71aeea3532549b46c50794c29694c0ce9565990e","tid":1392550,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"咁警察通例呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n違犯晒都冇事喎，幾時嚴肅追究？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a577effcb584a103f954346d464a47d278a2a4","tid":1392550,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"標題富有426社論的味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5af8b4e84f1e38625876fa8a9700cda5020b55","tid":1392550,"uid"